Definition: time during which clocks are set one hour ahead of local standard time
Example: widely adopted during summer to provide extra daylight in the evenings
Synonyms: daylight-savings_time, daylight_saving, daylight_savings, noun, Tops, time, during, which, clocks, are, set, one, hour, ahead, of, local, standard, widely, adopted, summer, to, provide, extra, daylight, in, the, evenings
Category: noun.time
